<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - PhuKien247</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
          crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <!-- Swiper.js CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <!-- AOS (Animate On Scroll) CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css" asp-append-version="true" />

    <style>
        /* ============================================
           CSS CUSTOM PROPERTIES
           ============================================ */
        :root {
            --pk-orange: #FF6B35;
            --pk-orange-dark: #e55a26;
            --pk-orange-light: #ff8f65;
            --pk-dark: #1a1a2e;
            --pk-dark-2: #16213e;
            --pk-gray: #f8f9fa;
            --pk-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pk-orange) 0%, var(--pk-orange-light) 100%);
            --pk-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            --pk-shadow-hover: 0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
            --pk-radius: 16px;
            --pk-transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
        }

        /* ============================================
           GLOBAL RESET & BASE
           ============================================ */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        main {
            flex: 1;
        }

        ::selection {
            background-color: var(--pk-orange);
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* ============================================
           LOADING SPINNER
           ============================================ */
        .page-loader {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: #fff;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 99999;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease, visibility 0.5s ease;
        }

        .page-loader.loaded {
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
        }

        .spinner {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border: 4px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 4px solid var(--pk-orange);
            border-radius: 50%;
            animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        /* ============================================
           NAVBAR - GLASSMORPHISM
           ============================================ */
        .navbar-pk {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
            padding: 0.6rem 0;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            z-index: 1050;
        }

        .navbar-pk.scrolled {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 0.4rem 0;
        }

        .navbar-pk .navbar-brand {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--pk-orange) !important;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
        }

        .navbar-pk .navbar-brand:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .navbar-pk .navbar-brand i {
            margin-right: 6px;
        }

        .navbar-pk .nav-link {
            color: var(--pk-dark) !important;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem !important;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }

        .navbar-pk .nav-link::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .navbar-pk .nav-link:hover::after,
        .navbar-pk .nav-link.active::after {
            width: 70%;
        }

        .navbar-pk .nav-link:hover,
        .navbar-pk .nav-link.active {
            color: var(--pk-orange) !important;
        }

        /* Cart icon badge */
        .cart-link {
            position: relative;
        }

        .cart-badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: -4px;
            right: -4px;
            background: var(--pk-orange);
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            animation: badgePulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        @@keyframes badgePulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.15); }
        }

        /* Animated hamburger */
        .navbar-toggler {
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem;
            position: relative;
            width: 36px;
            height: 36px;
        }

        .navbar-toggler:focus {
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .hamburger {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            width: 24px;
            height: 24px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .hamburger span {
            display: block;
            width: 24px;
            height: 2.5px;
            background-color: var(--pk-dark);
            border-radius: 2px;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            position: absolute;
        }

        .hamburger span:nth-child(1) { top: 4px; }
        .hamburger span:nth-child(2) { top: 11px; }
        .hamburger span:nth-child(3) { top: 18px; }

        .navbar-toggler[aria-expanded="true"] .hamburger span:nth-child(1) {
            top: 11px;
            transform: rotate(45deg);
        }

        .navbar-toggler[aria-expanded="true"] .hamburger span:nth-child(2) {
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-10px);
        }

        .navbar-toggler[aria-expanded="true"] .hamburger span:nth-child(3) {
            top: 11px;
            transform: rotate(-45deg);
        }

        /* ============================================
           NAVBAR SEARCH
           ============================================ */
        .nav-search {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 220px;
            min-width: 160px;
        }
        .nav-search input {
            border-radius: 50px;
            border: 1.5px solid #e5e7eb;
            background: #f9fafb;
            padding: 0.5rem 2.4rem 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.88rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            width: 100%;
        }
        .nav-search input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--pk-orange);
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255,107,53,0.12);
        }
        .nav-search button {
            position: absolute;
            right: 4px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            border: none;
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            color: #fff;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
        }
        .nav-search button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255,107,53,0.35);
        }
        @@media (max-width: 1199.98px) {
            .nav-search {
                max-width: 100%;
                margin: 0.5rem 0;
            }
        }

        /* ============================================
           BUTTONS
           ============================================ */
        .btn-pk {
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            border: none;
            color: #fff;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .btn-pk::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 50%;
            left: 50%;
            width: 0;
            height: 0;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            transition: width 0.6s ease, height 0.6s ease;
        }

        .btn-pk:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pk-orange-dark) 0%, var(--pk-orange) 100%);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-pk:hover::before {
            width: 300px;
            height: 300px;
        }

        .btn-pk-outline {
            border: 2px solid var(--pk-orange);
            color: var(--pk-orange);
            background: transparent;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .btn-pk-outline:hover {
            background: var(--pk-orange);
            color: #fff;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
        }

        .badge-pk {
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
        }

        /* ============================================
           GLOBAL CARD HOVER EFFECTS
           ============================================ */
        .card {
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            border: none;
            border-radius: var(--pk-radius);
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: var(--pk-shadow);
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-8px);
            box-shadow: var(--pk-shadow-hover);
        }

        /* ============================================
           FOOTER - GRADIENT DARK
           ============================================ */
        .footer-pk {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c29 0%, #1a1a2e 40%, #302b63 100%);
            color: #ccc;
            padding: 4rem 0 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .footer-pk::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -100px;
            right: -100px;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,107,53,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .footer-pk::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -150px;
            left: -100px;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,107,53,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .footer-pk h5 {
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
        }

        .footer-pk h5::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 40px;
            height: 3px;
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .footer-pk a {
            color: #aaa;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .footer-pk a:hover {
            color: var(--pk-orange);
            padding-left: 4px;
        }

        /* Social icons with hover animations */
        .footer-pk .social-icons a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: #fff;
            margin-right: 10px;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .footer-pk .social-icons a:hover {
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            transform: translateY(-4px) rotate(5deg);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.3);
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        /* Newsletter form */
        .newsletter-form {
            position: relative;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .newsletter-form input {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 0.7rem 1.2rem;
            padding-right: 120px;
            color: #fff;
            width: 100%;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
        }

        .newsletter-form input::placeholder {
            color: #888;
        }

        .newsletter-form input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--pk-orange);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.15);
        }

        .newsletter-form button {
            position: absolute;
            right: 4px;
            top: 4px;
            bottom: 4px;
            border: none;
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 0 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
        }

        .newsletter-form button:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
        }

        .footer-bottom {
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 2.5rem;
        }

        /* ============================================
           BACK TO TOP BUTTON
           ============================================ */
        .back-to-top {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 30px;
            right: 30px;
            width: 48px;
            height: 48px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--pk-gradient);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.4);
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: var(--pk-transition);
            z-index: 1040;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .back-to-top.visible {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .back-to-top:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(255, 107, 53, 0.5);
        }

        /* ============================================
           GLOBAL ANIMATIONS
           ============================================ */
        @@keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @@keyframes slideInLeft {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateX(-30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateX(0);
            }
        }

        @@keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }

        @@keyframes shimmer {
            0% { background-position: -200% 0; }
            100% { background-position: 200% 0; }
        }

        /* ============================================
           RESPONSIVE
           ============================================ */
        @@media (max-width: 1199.98px) {
            .navbar-pk .navbar-collapse {
                background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
                backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
                border-radius: 12px;
                padding: 1rem;
                margin-top: 0.5rem;
                box-shadow: var(--pk-shadow);
            }
        }
    </style>

    @await RenderSectionAsync("Styles", required: false)
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Page Loader -->
    <div class="page-loader" id="pageLoader">
        <div class="spinner"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-xl navbar-pk sticky-top" id="mainNav">
        <div class="container-fluid px-3 px-lg-4">
            <a class="navbar-brand" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>PhuKien247
            </a>

            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#mainNavbar"
                    aria-controls="mainNavbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <div class="hamburger">
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                    <span></span>
                </div>
            </button>

            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mainNavbar">
                <ul class="navbar-nav me-auto mb-2 mb-xl-0 align-items-xl-center">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                            <i class="fas fa-home me-1"></i>Trang ch&#7911;
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="Index">
                            <i class="fas fa-box-open me-1"></i>S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="RepairService" asp-action="Index">
                            <i class="fas fa-tools me-1"></i>D&#7883;ch v&#7909; s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" asp-controller="Tracking" asp-action="Index">
                            <i class="fas fa-search-location me-1"></i>Tra c&#7913;u
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item dropdown">
                        <a class="nav-link dropdown-toggle" href="#" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                            <i class="fas fa-headset me-1"></i>H&#7895; tr&#7907;
                        </a>
                        <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="About"><i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>Gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Faq"><i class="fas fa-question-circle me-2"></i>C&acirc;u h&#7887;i th&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7863;p</a></li>
                            <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact"><i class="fas fa-envelope me-2"></i>Li&ecirc;n h&#7879;</a></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link cart-link" asp-controller="Cart" asp-action="Index">
                            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart me-1"></i>Gi&#7887; h&agrave;ng
                            <span class="cart-badge" id="cartBadge" style="display:none;">0</span>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <!-- Global Search -->
                <form class="nav-search me-xl-3" method="get" asp-controller="Product" asp-action="Index" role="search">
                    <input type="text" name="search" class="form-control" placeholder="T&igrave;m s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m..." autocomplete="off" />
                    <button type="submit" title="T&igrave;m ki&#7871;m"><i class="fas fa-search"></i></button>
                </form>

                <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-2">
                    @if (User.Identity != null && User.Identity.IsAuthenticated)
                    {
                        @if (User.IsInRole("Admin"))
                        {
                            <a asp-area="Admin" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary">
                                <i class="fas fa-cog me-1"></i>Qu&#7843;n tr&#7883;
                            </a>
                        }
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <button class="btn btn-sm btn-pk dropdown-toggle" type="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                                <i class="fas fa-user me-1"></i>@User.Identity.Name
                            </button>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-end">
                                <li>
                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Profile" asp-action="Index">
                                        <i class="fas fa-id-card me-2"></i>H&#7891; s&#417; c&#7911;a t&ocirc;i
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Profile" asp-action="ChangePassword">
                                        <i class="fas fa-key me-2"></i>&#272;&#7893;i m&#7853;t kh&#7849;u
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="Order" asp-action="MyOrders">
                                        <i class="fas fa-clipboard-list me-2"></i>&#272;&#417;n h&agrave;ng
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="RepairService" asp-action="MyBookings">
                                        <i class="fas fa-tools me-2"></i>L&#7883;ch s&#7917;a c&#7911;a t&ocirc;i
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                                <li><hr class="dropdown-divider" /></li>
                                <li>
                                    <form asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Logout" method="post" class="px-0">
                                        <button type="submit" class="dropdown-item text-danger">
                                            <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt me-2"></i>&#272;&#259;ng xu&#7845;t
                                        </button>
                                    </form>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login" class="btn btn-sm btn-pk-outline">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt me-1"></i>&#272;&#259;ng nh&#7853;p
                        </a>
                        <a asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register" class="btn btn-sm btn-pk">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus me-1"></i>&#272;&#259;ng k&yacute;
                        </a>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Main content -->
    <main>
        @RenderBody()
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="footer-pk">
        <div class="container position-relative" style="z-index: 1;">
            <div class="row g-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
                    <h5><i class="fas fa-mobile-alt me-2"></i>PhuKien247</h5>
                    <p class="mb-3">Chuy&ecirc;n cung c&#7845;p ph&#7909; ki&#7879;n &#273;i&#7879;n tho&#7841;i ch&iacute;nh h&atilde;ng v&agrave; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; s&#7917;a ch&#7919;a uy t&iacute;n t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam. Ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i cam k&#7871;t mang &#273;&#7871;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7899;i gi&aacute; c&#7843; h&#7907;p l&yacute; nh&#7845;t.</p>
                    <div class="social-icons">
                        <a href="#" title="Facebook"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" title="Instagram"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" title="TikTok"><i class="fab fa-tiktok"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" title="YouTube"><i class="fab fa-youtube"></i></a>
                        <a href="#" title="Zalo"><i class="fas fa-comment-dots"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-2 col-md-6" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                    <h5>Li&ecirc;n k&#7871;t</h5>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled">
                        <li class="mb-2"><a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right me-1 small"></i>Trang ch&#7911;</a></li>
                        <li class="mb-2"><a asp-controller="Product" asp-action="Index"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right me-1 small"></i>S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m</a></li>
